    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/1e52f705f17f60d0c26b7696fab4dc93.poster.avif?t=1759443824\" width=800 height=46 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/1e52f705f17f60d0c26b7696fab4dc93.webm?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/1e52f705f17f60d0c26b7696fab4dc93.mp4?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/1ba9a56dbee4f9a70be0827b25b976ff.avif?t=1759443824\" width=800 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring your game characters to life with <strong>Retro Character Creator Tool</strong>. This easy-to-use tool lets you create 4-directional characters with a wide variety of hair styles, clothing options, and accessories choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>Retro Character Creator Tool</strong> features a user-friendly interface, making it easy for even beginners to create unique and engaging characters for their game. The tool includes a vast library of assets,  all designed in a charming pixel art style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/9be4e2728585bf408824f7d9aa500ee0.poster.avif?t=1759443824\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/9be4e2728585bf408824f7d9aa500ee0.webm?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/9be4e2728585bf408824f7d9aa500ee0.mp4?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Character Sprite Settings:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walking sprite with 4 frames!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Idle sprite with 4 frames!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attack sprite with 4 frames!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Static Dead Sprite!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Directions (Left, Right, Up, Down)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Countless clothes and accessories pieces!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Layers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25 Basic colors!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable colors available!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compatible with any game engine, including RPG Maker!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/02ed8d4e7e7668f4535d4e433daba57e.poster.avif?t=1759443824\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/02ed8d4e7e7668f4535d4e433daba57e.webm?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/02ed8d4e7e7668f4535d4e433daba57e.mp4?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Face Sprite Settings:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >48x48 Pixels Sprite!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >192x192 Pixels Sprite for RPG Maker!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compatible with any game engine, including RPG Maker!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/1fa77d608cbe89e5e2b9b48d45e57c59.poster.avif?t=1759443824\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/1fa77d608cbe89e5e2b9b48d45e57c59.webm?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/1fa77d608cbe89e5e2b9b48d45e57c59.mp4?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tool Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save your character sprites at any time!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Load your saved character sprites!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Export for the designed game engine!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Import and use at your game projects!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Check out some examples below of the character sprites being used in an actual game!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/71e9e809cb5f201637b2383c6870dcab.poster.avif?t=1759443824\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/71e9e809cb5f201637b2383c6870dcab.webm?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/71e9e809cb5f201637b2383c6870dcab.mp4?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/027815e2f49b8ce682c2cae1faee958c.poster.avif?t=1759443824\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/027815e2f49b8ce682c2cae1faee958c.webm?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/027815e2f49b8ce682c2cae1faee958c.mp4?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/f99b8f331f223c1d35fbf850c48b61a4.poster.avif?t=1759443824\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/f99b8f331f223c1d35fbf850c48b61a4.webm?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/f99b8f331f223c1d35fbf850c48b61a4.mp4?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/19590bcf0fbd1e1a64539b8d3876da7b.poster.avif?t=1759443824\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/19590bcf0fbd1e1a64539b8d3876da7b.webm?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/19590bcf0fbd1e1a64539b8d3876da7b.mp4?t=1759443824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop